{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "Jilo com Jurubeba API",
		"description": "Colecao Postman para a API do sistema de gestao de restaurantes Jilo com Jurubeba.\n\nTech Challenge FIAP Pos-Tech Fase 2 - Grupo 3.\n\n**Como usar:**\n1. Execute a request \"Login\" para obter o token JWT automaticamente.\n2. Todas as demais requests autenticadas ja utilizam o token salvo na variavel `{{token}}`.\n\n**Profiles de banco:**\n- Default: H2 em memoria\n- `dev`: MySQL via Docker\n- `postgres`: PostgreSQL\n\n**Swagger UI:** http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Endpoints de autenticacao e geracao de token JWT.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Token JWT salvo com sucesso!\");",
									"}",
									"",
									"pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test(\"Response has token\", function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"token\");",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.token).to.be.a(\"string\").and.not.empty;",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"admin@jilocomjurubeba.com\",\n    \"senha\": \"admin123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						},
						"description": "Autentica um usuario e retorna um token JWT.\n\nO token e salvo automaticamente na variavel de colecao `{{token}}` para uso nas demais requests."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
